data.description: ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 2.75% - BUYER MUST QUALIFY FOR VA LOAN. Beautiful 5 acre parcel with pond, 2 car detached garage and large barn with multiple storage bays. This brick ranch features a light filled living room, 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, and laundry room on the main level with two full kitchens - great for potential in-law suite in the basement with dedicated entrance, separate full bathroom, washer and dryer hook ups on each level. Covered wrap around deck overlooks beautiful views. All kitchen appliances, washer, dryer, mower, tiller and grill to remain. Home inspections are welcomed however the property is sold as-is.
